
	JSE-listed Huge Group has appointed MTN deputy CFO Gunter Engling MD of Huge Telecom. 
	His appointment will be effective April 1, 2018, following the completion of his notice period with MTN. 
	Engling has served 14 years with MTN, with roles spanning acting group CFO; MTN Rwanda CEO; MTN Ghana CFO; and MTN Nigeria GM financial planning. 
	He holds a Bachelor of Commerce in Accounting (Honours) and CTA from Stellenbosch University.Â 